quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  51,24,Kodi udamva nkhani ya alendo olemekezeka a Abrahamu
  51,25,"Pamene iwo adadza kwa iye, iwo adati, “Mtendere.” Ndipo iye adati, “Mtendere.” Ndipo iye adati, “Inu ndinu alendo kwa ine.”"
  51,26,Ndipo iye atapita ku banja lake adabweretsa nyama ya ng’ombe yowotcha
  51,27,"Motero iye adadza nayo kwa iwo nati, “Kodi simufuna kudya?”"
  51,28,"Motero iye adayamba kuchita mantha mu mtima mwake. Ndipo iwo adati, “Usaope.” Ndipo iwo adamuuza nkhani yabwino yakubadwa kwa mwana wamwamuna yemwe adzakhala wanzeru kwambiri"
  51,29,"Ndipo mkazi wake adadza modzichepetsa ndipo adamenya pa mphumi pake nati, “Nkhalamba yaikazi yosaberekapo!”"
  51,30,"Iwo adati, “Ngakhale ndi choncho, Ambuye wako wayankhula. Iye ndi wodzala ndi luntha ndiponso nzeru.”"
  51,31,"Iye adati, “Kodi inu Atumwi uthenga wanu ndi wotani?”"
  51,32,"Iwo adati, “Ife tatumidwa kwa anthu ochimwa.”"
  51,33,“Kuti tigwetse pa iwo miyala yamakande.”
  51,34,“Idakonzedwa ndi Ambuye wako kudza kwa anthu oswa malamulo.”
  51,35,Ndipo Ife tidatulutsa anthu okhulupirira amene adali momwemo
  51,36,Koma sitidapezemo mabanja a Chisilamu kupatula banja limodzi lokha basi
  51,37,Ndipo Ife tidasiyamo chizindikiro kwa iwo amene amaopa chilango chowawa
  51,38,Ndi mwa Mose. Pamene tidamutumiza kwa Farawo ndi zizindikiro zooneka
  51,39,"Koma Farawo adakana pamodzi ndi mafumu ake nati, “Ndiwe munthu wamatsenga kapena munthu wa misala.”"
  51,40,Motero tidamugwira pamodzi ndi gulu la asirikali ake ndi kuwamiza onse m’nyanja pamene iye ndiye adali wolakwa
  51,41,Ndipo mwa a Aad pamene tidawatumizira mphepo yoononga
  51,42,Imene sidasiye chilichonse chimene idalimbana nacho kupatula kuchiononga ndi kuchisandutsa phulusa
  51,43,"Ndipo mwa anthu a Thamoud. Pamene adauzidwa kuti, “Basangalalani kanthawi kochepa.”"
  51,44,"Koma iwo adaphwanya lamulo la Ambuye wawo mwamwano, kotero mabingu adawaononga iwo ali kuona"
  51,45,Kotero iwo adalibe mphamvu zodzuka kapena zodzitetezera
  51,46,Ndi anthu a Nowa iwo asanadze. Ndithudi iwo adali anthu oswa malamulo